- AI/train/train.py:16: updated default batch size from 2 to 4.
- AI/train/train.py:19: updated default initial learning rate `lr0` from 1e-4 to 1e-3.
- Reran dataset preprocessing using command: `.venv\Scripts\python AI/preprocess/preprocess.py --good-ratio 0.1 --augment-count 3` resulting in 1375 processed samples (1258 defect + 117 good background) and 2643 defect-only augmented train samples.
- Verified balanced dataset using a training smoke-test.

